Introduction

SeoYeon is a South Korean singer and actress under MODHAUS. Best known for being a member of the girl group tripleS, she was introduced as the first member on May 1, 2022. She made her debut on February 13, 2023, with the mini album "ASSEMBLE". As a member of tripleS, SeoYeon has been in the sub-units +(KR)ystal Eyes, ACID EYES, and LOVElution.

Besides her activities with tripleS, she was a contestant on Mnet's survival show "Queendom Puzzle". However, she was eliminated after ranking 24th. She also debuted as an actress in September 2024 with her lead role in the web drama 'What Summer Likes!'.
